The paper discusses the use of AI and automation in IT support services, specifically in incident management. It focuses on the analysis of multi-modal content, including text and images, to improve ticket routing and resolution. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
